<title>SOUTH AFRICA: LITHOSAVER CORRECTS YR EPS FIGURE.</title>
<headline>LITHOSAVER CORRECTS YR EPS FIGURE.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Lithosaver Systems Ltd said on Thursday the correct figure for earnings per share before exceptional items was 33.2 cents for the year ended February 1997 instead of the 38.5 cents published on May 6.</p>
<p>It said the published amount excluded tax on the exceptional item. </p>
<p>There is no effect on earnings per share after the exceptional item.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom, +27 11 482 1003</p>
